Description: Fix CVE-2026-54371: symlink traversal in getfattr/setfattr
 Harden getfattr and setfattr with AT_SYMLINK_NOFOLLOW and
 openat2(RESOLVE_NO_SYMLINKS). Fix setfattr --restore path handling.
Author: Andreas Gruenbacher <agruenba@redhat.com>
Origin: upstream, https://git.savannah.nongnu.org/git/attr.git
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2026-07-03
